OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773133489
OL,3,CNature's calendar has gone rogue:
OL,4,CEarly blooms signal changing UK Springs
OL,6,FA major study from the University of
OL,7,FCambridge, using hundreds of thousands
OL,8,Fof volunteer observations, found that
OL,9,Fplants like snowdrops, hazel, and
OL,10,Fcrocuses now flower around a month
OL,11,Fearlier than they did in the 18th
OL,12,Fcentury.
OL,14,FThis field of study ` phenology `
OL,15,Ftracks the timing of natural events,
OL,16,Fand it's one of the clearest,
OL,17,Frealworld signals of climate change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
