OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773133489
OL,3,CNature's calendar has gone rogue:
OL,4,CEarly blooms signal changing UK Springs
OL,6,FLong-term records from the Nature's
OL,7,FCalendar project run by the Woodland
OL,8,FTrust show first flowering dates
OL,9,Fshifting steadily earlier, and
OL,10,Fofficial data from the UK Met Office
OL,11,Fconfirms that spring temperatures are
OL,12,Fnow among the fastestwarming of any
OL,13,Fseason in the UK.
OL,15,FWhich plants will I see blooming early?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
