PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773133489
OL,3,CNature's calendar has gone rogue:
OL,4,CEarly blooms signal changing UK Springs
OL,6,FWhen flowers appear early due to
OL,7,Fwarmer springs, the rest of the
OL,8,Fnatural world has to keep up.
OL,10,FIf they don't, it can lead to what
OL,11,Fscientists call an ecological mismatch
OL,12,F` species falling out of sync with the
OL,13,Fseasonal cues they've relied on for
OL,14,Fmillennia.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
