PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773133489
OL,3,CNature's calendar has gone rogue:
OL,4,CEarly blooms signal changing UK Springs
OL,6,FEssentially, with the season starting
OL,7,Fearlier in the year than it used to,
OL,8,Fthose tender shoots and buds are
OL,9,Fincredibly vulnerable to the very
OL,10,Fnormal temperature fluctuations early
OL,11,FSpring.
OL,13,FTemperatures are expected to drop away
OL,14,Flater this week - particularly
OL,15,Fovernight - and that risks the
OL,16,Fsurvival of those early plants, which
OL,17,Fin turn, threatens the insects and
OL,18,Fwildlife that depend on them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
